{"id":620903,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/【立此存照】发维尼xiong-涉嫌传播恶性谣言/","date":"2019-10-28T07:12:50Z","modified":"2019-10-28T07:12:50Z","title":"【立此存照】发“维尼xiong” 涉嫌传播恶性谣言","content":"<p>10月26日，有推特网友爆料，自己在某微信群内谈及区块链内容时候，在分享习近平相关新闻后发布了一条包含“维尼xiong”的评论消息，遭到微信官方封号，理由是：涉嫌传播恶性谣言。</p>\n<p>@frankyuyong：一句维尼xiong，微信账号没有了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EHxk-6YWkAEdDNM.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-620904\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EHxk-6YWkAEdDNM.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"416\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EHxk-6YWkAEdDNM.jpg 416w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EHxk-6YWkAEdDNM-139x300.jpg 139w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 416px) 100vw, 416px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EHxk-6YXYAAW7w8.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-620905\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EHxk-6YXYAAW7w8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"415\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EHxk-6YXYAAW7w8.jpg 415w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EHxk-6YXYAAW7w8-138x300.jpg 138w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 415px) 100vw, 415px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"zoX8lgg5wE\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e6%89%b9%e9%87%8f%e5%b0%81%e5%8f%b7-%e5%be%ae%e4%bf%a1%e5%b0%81%e5%bb%ba%e6%97%b6%e4%bb%a3%e5%88%b0%e6%9d%a5/\">【立此存照】批量封号 微信“封建”时代到来</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【立此存照】批量封号 微信“封建”时代到来》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e6%89%b9%e9%87%8f%e5%b0%81%e5%8f%b7-%e5%be%ae%e4%bf%a1%